*[http://ntrs.nasa.gov/search.jsp?Ne=26&amp;Ntt=Apollo+11&amp;Ntk=Keywords&amp;Ntx=mode+matchall&amp;N=269&amp;Ns=HarvestDate|1&amp;as=false Apollo 11 repository on NASA National Technical Reports Server]

