*[[Animal (2001 film)|''Animal'' (2001 film)]], Argentine film by Sergio Bizzio with Carlos Roffé
*[[Animal (2005 film)|''Animal'' (2005 film)]], US film by David J. Burke with Ving Rhames and Terrance Howard

