{{main|List of cities in Aruba}}
The island, with a population of just over 100,000 inhabitants, does not have major cities.

* [[Oranjestad, Aruba|Oranjestad]] (33,000 in 2006)
* [[Paradera]]
* [[San Nicolas]]
* [[Noord]]
* [[Santa Cruz, Aruba|Santa Cruz]]
