{{Spaces|2}}&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:90%;&quot;&gt;* Collapsed September 2, 2005 &lt;ref&gt;{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/news/world/2005-09-02-aruba-bridge_x.htm?csp=36|title=Coral bridge, natural Aruba tourist spot, collapses|publisher=''[[Associated Press]]''|year=2005|accessdate=2010-09-11}}&lt;/ref&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

